hopobject.body: Which year are you in? cytotec available in sri lanka Under Article 66 of the SME Promotion Act, the government is required to replenish the SME Fund deficits when the fund's reserves are not sufficient to absorb its losses. State support is also evidenced by the annual capital contribution by the government, which helps the fund to partially cover operating losses arising from the negative interest rate spread. Fitch expects losses to remain around KRW200bn per annum over the medium term.
